comment: Beal (WAS) does not jump vertically when contesting the layup attempt by Mirotic (CHI).
Contact by Snell (CHI) on Wall (WAS) as he drives to the basket does not affect his RSBQ.
Mirotic (CHI) jumps vertically while in the restricted area to contest Wall's (WAS) layup attempt. The contact causes Mirotic (CHI) to move backwards after contact.
Brooks' (CHI) heel remains above the boundary line and does not go OOBs.
Wall (WAS) impedes Brooks' (CHI) progress on the play to the basket, and a blocking foul should have been called.
Gortat (WAS) pushes Mirotic (CHI) in the back.
Noah (CHI) makes contact with the body and head of Porter (WAS) from behind as Porter attempts his shot.
Temple (WAS) clamps the arm of Gasol (CHI) preventing him from securing the rebound.
Gortat (WAS) sets an illegal screen as he moves with the defender and uses his arms to prevent Snell (CHI) from being able to defend the shooter.
